title: Oxfordshire hosts successful Young Carers Conference (Oxfordshire County Council)
text: ( Source : Oxfordshire County Council ) Public service representatives from the county and surrounding areas took part in workshops and presentations to share knowledge on issues affecting children who have to care for a family member at home .
